13:
Was that... a dream?
And that voice... Why HIM of all
people?
16:
Captain Zegra's old stuff? Why is it
glowing...
19:
Breaking news! The pirate legend
long thought gone has resurfaced!
Items belonging to the famous
Captain Zegra have been
discovered.
21:
Managers of Paradise Isle have
officially announced that this
precious treasure will be available
as a prize at the resort's casino—
28:
Ahh, finally, a proper vacation! I
can't remember the last time I got a
chance to relax... Time to take it
easy—
38:
Marina! How many times have we
had this conversation? You NEED to
knock on doors before entering!
42:
Hehehe. What's wrong Alk? Scared I'll
find something incriminating in your
room?
Anyway, I've got important things to
discuss.
50:
Huh? Have you never seen a
swimsuit before? People wear them
when it's HOT outside! Like it
currently is now.
54:
R-right. That makes sense. I
guess.
Anyway I just realized I have a...
thing. A thing where I need to leave
the room right now.
58:
Oh my, what's the matter?
Something's got you all flustered all
of a sudden. I wonder what it could
be! Hehe.
66:
Sorry, sorry! You're just so cute when
you squirm. Well then, let's get going!
73:
On vacation! To the resort!
And finally... on an adventure!
82:
Drifting on the sea! Now this is the
life!
87: I didn't sign up for this!
